data.title: List of Songs by The Monkees
data.meta_description: An alternate mix of 'Auntie's Municipal Court' which features Michael Nesmith on lead vocals with Micky Dolenz on harmony, was included on The Birds, the Bees and the Monkees: Deluxe Edition. An early mix of 'Can You Dig It?' which features Peter Tork on lead vocals was included on the 1994...
